headline: Pegasystems Set to Join S&P MidCap 400
summary: Pegasystems Inc. (NASD: PEGA) will replace Nordstrom Inc. (NYSE: JWN) in the S&P MidCap 400 effective prior to the opening of trading on Thursday, May 22. The Nordstrom family and El Puerto de Liverpool S.A.B. de C.V. (BMV: LIVEPOL) are acquiring Nordstrom in a deal expected to be completed on May 20.
